      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA procedures documented in accordance with FDA 21 CFR Part 820 QSR; simulation software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1) version-controlled and validated per IQ/OQ/PQ protocol. Gradation 2 requires documented SQA plan with traceability to solver version.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 was used under a documented software quality assurance plan satisfying FDA 21 CFR Part 820 requirements. Installation qualification and operational qualification records confirm solver version integrity. Required Gradation 2 is achieved."
    },
    {
